t insert tags</a><br><br>Below this paragraph you can see the &#34;personal data&#34; module in action. This module allows front end users to change their personal data. Make sure to cross-check all changes in the back end.</p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', 'sourceText', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 4, 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', 0x00000000000000000000000000000000, '', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, 0, '');
