an access level parameter.</p>\n<p>And the same goes for the back end users. Create one group that has only the right to edit calendar entries, another one that is only allowed to write articles and a third one that has access to both.</p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', 'sourceText', NULL, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, NULL, 0, 4, 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', 0x00000000000000000000000000000000, '', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 0, '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, 0, '');
