, e.g. resizing or even cropping it and to add a link to a contao page, to an external URI or to a full resolution version of the image. You can define wether the linked page will be opened in a new window or tab of your browser. The full resolution version of the image will be opened in an overlay on the same page if defined that way in the page layout.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0x6862eac0a88b11eda7051d513e439626, 'Adding an image to a text element', 'Adding an image to a text element', 'a:3:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";i:2;s:1:\"1\";}', NULL, 1, 'Adding an image to a text element', 'below', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', 'sourceText', NULL, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, NULL, 0, 4, 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', 0x00000000000000000000000000000000, '', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:12:\"divider--top\";}', 0, '', '', 'ascending', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'com_default', NULL, 0, '');
