ting a specific slide as the starting point, the counting starts at 0</li>\n<li>Continous:&nbsp;Make the slider start all over when reaching the end</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can see the slider in action on the&nbsp;<a title=\"{{link_title::2|attr}}\" href=\"{{link_url::2|urlattr}}\">homepage</a>.</p>\n<p>To use it, jQuery or Mootools need to be enabled in the page layout and the corresponding j- or moo-template has to be added as well.</p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ascending', '', '', '', '', 'sourceText', NULL, '', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, NULL, 0, 4, 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', NULL, '', '', 0x00000000000000000000000000000000, '', NULL, 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 300, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:\"\";i:1;s:0:\"\";}', 0, '', '', 'ascending', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'com_default', NULL, 0, '');
